### Get API Info
GET http://localhost:5000

### Add Expense
POST http://localhost:5000/expense
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 45.50,
  "description": "Starbucks coffee"
}
### Set Budget
POST http://localhost:5000/budget
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "food",
  "amount": 50
}
### Add Food Expense (Over Budget!)
POST http://localhost:5000/expense
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00,
  "description": "Pizza dinner"
}